Class ShutdownCli

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.seagullsw.appinterface.server.admin.ShutdownCli
  • public final class ShutdownCli
extends Object
    Stops the AIS.

    Command Line Interface

    The usage syntax is: 
     com.seagullsw.appinterface.server.admin.client.ShutdownCli -d | -c <file> | -h
  -u,--url <url>           Specifies the server URL: protocol://address:port where protocol is tcp or http.
  -h,--help                Prints this message and exits
